{"tid":2229292,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【手機JJ】Among us 香港區上線啦！","createTime":"2020-10-04T09:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T05:06:22.000Z","uid":138232,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"21d5a99b212f1a2a26ee7013923cd88e249886ea","tid":2229292,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W9q_L-Zd5IM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW9q_L-Zd5IM&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=2f290b0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W9q_L-Zd5IM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vQEJBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vQEJBj.jpg&h=dc6ff060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《 Among US》是一款狼人殺類游戲，遊戲場景發生在一艘太空船上，遊戲分為兩個陣營。一個是船員陣營（好人），另外一個是冒充者（狼人）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n船員陣營：<br />\n<br />\n船員可以透過完成所有的飛船建設任務（隨機小遊戲)，或者通過投票將所有冒充者扔出airlock（被投票出去的人會有被丟出飛船的動畫）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 冒充者陣營：<br />\n<br />\n冒充者同樣有兩種獲勝方式，一個是通過破壞飛船關鍵部件的限時任務，如果在規定時間內船員沒有完成對應任務則冒充者直接獲得勝利。<br />\n<br />\n 另外一種獲勝方式是不斷殺害船員，直到冒充者人數與船員一致，則獲得勝利。<br />\n<br />\nAmong us香港區Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/251767009568982/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F251767009568982%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=6fb8554f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/251767009568982/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\nAmong us香港區Discord Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/NKtA3R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.com%2Finvite%2FNKtA3R&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=6ed4925b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.com/invite/NKtA3R</a><br />\n<br />\nAmong us香港區WhatsApp Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/IfcyjY2pNw9Be7qbNpy0XD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.